oves sign-invariance. Empirical contract validation deferred to P1-IMPL's RED test by design.\",\n    \"D7 — Confirmed second writer site at Engine::write_vector_for_test (lib.rs:1806-1845, insert at :1838); Pack 1 must update both sites in lockstep.\",\n    \"D8 — Reader at read_search_in_tx (lib.rs:2317-2323) is provably no-op under schema extension: embedding column type unchanged; metadata blog confirms additional vec0 columns do not alter MATCH semantics on the original vector column. AC-013 latency stays at 2048/2327 ms post-Pack 1.\"\n  ],\n  \"blockers_encountered\": [],\n  \"additional_changes_made_in_scope\": [],\n  \"agent_verify_result\": \"skipped (doc-only slice)\",\n  \"next_step_for_orchestrator\": \"spawn codex reviewer on the Pack 1 design memo\"\n}\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":512,"cache_read_input_tokens":80705,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":512},"output_tokens":54,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8d9c2010-470a-469e-a899-a4db3c31910c","uuid":"932c5b3d-7d51-4769-9053-e63418acd9f6","request_id":"req_011CbT9mBmtnmSRN4THKweoy"}
