    38	    (caller-supplied pyo3/napi embedders are `Sync`-only by contract and may not
    39	    be concurrency-safe), not throughput — it is throughput-neutral on the
    40	    candle default (candle uses one process-wide rayon pool; the earlier "~13×"
    41	    throughput rationale was withdrawn).
