1. `BLOCK` — [Cargo.toml](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/Cargo.toml:28) bumps Axis W to `0.7.1`, but the publish-time sibling dependency pins in the same file remain at `0.7.0` in [Cargo.toml](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/Cargo.toml:48). The file’s own comment says those `[workspace.dependencies]` entries are what `cargo publish` uses once `path` is stripped, and that Axis W entries “are bumped lockstep” with `[workspace.package].version` ([Cargo.toml](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/Cargo.toml:38)). The manifests do consume those workspace deps, e.g. [src/rust/crates/fathomdb/Cargo.toml](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb/Cargo.toml:11) and [src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/Cargo.toml](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/Cargo.toml:11). As written, a `0.7.1` publish would still declare sibling requirements on `0.7.0`, which violates the stated version policy for this slice.

Everything else I checked in the reviewed diff looked consistent with the requested focus: the 0.7.0 notes keep the recall gap explicit and not retconned ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:298)); the 0.937 correction is framed as 0.7.1+/0.7.2 hardening output, not as a retroactive 0.7.0 pass ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:137), [docs/embedder.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/docs/embedder.md:113)); migration and wipe-and-rewrite are clear ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:215), [docs/embedder.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/docs/embedder.md:129)); the `~133 MB` weight-set wording is honest and opt-in ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:177), [docs/embedder.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/docs/embedder.md:68)); Python/TS flag names match the bindings ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:148), [docs/embedder.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/docs/embedder.md:37), [src/python/fathomdb/engine.py](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/python/fathomdb/engine.py:60), [src/ts/src/index.ts](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/ts/src/index.ts:25)); dates are `2026-06-01`; `### Removed` sections are present; and `0.7.2` remains unreleased/in progress ([CHANGELOG.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/CHANGELOG.md:15)).

